osxscreenshot: ! "= SAVING\r\n\r\nCmd-Shift-3 - Take picture of the entire screen\r\nCmd-Shift-4
  - Take picture of selected area\r\n            - Hold Spacebar to move selected
  area (whilst dragging)\r\n            - Hold Shift to change size in one direction
  only\r\n            - Hold Option for centre-based resizing\r\n            - Press
  Spacebar and click window for just that window\r\n\r\n= COPYING\r\n\r\nTo copy images
  to the clipboard use the keystrokes above, but include Ctrl.\r\n"
